Because of the conflict between protobuf-java versions 2.5 and 3.5,  the field `memoizedSize`  is private of AbstractMessage.java in version 2.5，just like this:
`private int memoizedSize = -1;

  public int getSerializedSize() {
    int size = memoizedSize;
    if (size != -1) {
      return size;
    }
...
 `

version 3.5 work fine! 
so please delete protobuf-java-2.5.0.jar   ! 
